{"tid":2513841,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"尖沙咀不忘老細回應","createTime":"2021-05-03T00:43:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T01:06:14.000Z","uid":46003,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"86985d29a3dd62211e8866f6e93323085207e8fb","tid":2513841,"uid":46003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:43:28.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係不忘老細<br />\n<br />\n首先我想講下，不忘係點樣開始嘅。2019年個陣，機緣巧合之下，我遇到兩個年輕人(舊員工A先生為其中一個)，一個衝動但有幹勁嘅年輕人，和一個務實嘅年輕人，佢哋都係願意為左香港嘅未來，付出自己未來嘅人。可能有人會覺得我魯莽衝動，但從佢哋身上面，我睇到希望。我喺度諗，既然我有少少能力，我可唔可以為佢哋，做多少少呢？於是，我同佢哋講，我願意出錢買一個希望，畀佢哋兩個年輕人去嘗試營運一間小店，而呢個就係不忘嘅原形。<br />\n<br />\n有追post可能會留意到，我有一份正職，喺香港嚟講人工不算特別高，不過每個月或多或少都能夠補貼到不忘的營運開支。係，不忘一直都係蝕緊錢，但我覺得唔緊要， 由決定賣腸粉餃子嘅時候，我已經唔諗賺唔賺錢。<br />\n<br />\n家庭式經營嘅小食店本身就是一條難以經營的路，需要不斷投放資金同精力去維持，加上頭先都提過我有正職，我並不能夠經常喺舖頭出現。本住信任兩個年輕人嘅心，我除咗喺開舖初期落手落腳教佢哋點樣做，店內大小事務我都放手俾佢哋處理，話我天真都好，我總是希望終有一日佢地能夠成為獨當一面嘅人。但係對於鼠患問題，無論點講我都係責無旁貸嘅。當佢哋發現鼠患嘅時候，我有不斷跟進同埋吩咐佢哋兩位去聯絡滅鼠公司，過程我唔多講， 但自2020年11月起，滅鼠公司每星期都會嚟不忘進行滅鼠工作。<br />\n<br />\n我以為不忘開業一年以嚟，佢地經歷過大大小小嘅事，有能力處理呢個問題，但原來最後都係我不斷催促之下，問題先至得以改善。<br />\n<br />\n2021年，其中一個年輕人A先生(舊員工)，自新年之後工作態度變得消極。我發現，有啲日子係A先生連同3個兼職小朋友一共四人（唔計包餃姨姨），負責不忘嘅門面同外賣生意。佢哋有講過幾次，話工作太辛苦，但不忘其實只有兩張二人檯，而全日生意額都只有兩千左右。當然呢個生意額係連人工都cover唔到，我以為係生意難做。但係，喺無人番工的日子，我自己拎假去不忘on duty，生意額居然三千有多，隔離韓國舖老闆娘更話不忘經常排長龍，一日無可能得兩千嘅生意額。<br />\n<br />\n我嘗試唔去諗箇中原因，都無同A先生提過呢段插曲，只係默默地加強推廣網上生餃生意去維持門店運作。但好景不常（雖然開業以嚟都無賺過錢），夏天網上生餃銷量下降，加上中間發生好多事，我實在無辦法再花更多心神去同A先生溝通調和，亦無能力再貼更多嘅錢落去，我唯有解僱A先生，希望佢揾到另一個方向走自己嘅人生，畢竟信任不能當飯食，只係我無諗過最後卻換來如此的報復。<br />\n<br />\n我必須承認，自己唔係一個擅於溝通嘅人，經常會詞不達意，令其他人誤會。可能好多人會覺得我語氣唔好、態度差，但對朋友講嘢，我以為直截了當會比凡事客氣好，當然我都無諗過我心目中嘅朋友會quote一段勞工法例畀我，除左心寒，我真係唔知可以講咩。<br />\n<br />\n有關A先生嘅薪金問題，我無意拖欠任何人的薪酬，以往所有薪酬都是準時發放。惟今次有所爭拗，先會出現連登上面嘅post。因為MPF計算問題出現分歧，我首先喺4月26日過左HKD 7372畀A先生，以維持佢生活開支，然後先同佢商討MPF事宜，而尾數HKD4034已經喺5月2日付清。<br />\n<br />\n豬肉事宜上，不忘一直以來都用緊健康農場提供的泰國豬肉，圖中出示多個月來採購泰國豬肉嘅訂單。因為泰國豬肉嘅供應量不穩，有時候未能應付不忘嘅訂單，所以我們會購入少量貴價嘅中國豬肉嚟填補不足的份量。呢啲事情，其實A先生全部都知道。<br />\n<br />\n最後，非常抱歉這件事為大家帶來麻煩。不忘尚有不足之處，我對於今次的過失責無旁貸。接下來，不忘會聘請信譽良好、可靠嘅清潔公司加強處理衛生問題，並會好好反省過錯。多謝大家一直以來嘅支持。<br />\n<br />\n處理鼠患問題<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X407ODy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX407ODy.png&h=b11902d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yDbSfiy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyDbSfiy.png&h=ab3d8b3f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fDQ36qe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfDQ36qe.png&h=2d60332c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n關於薪金問題<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5usNOJt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5usNOJt.png&h=7b7072bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RqsmS6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRqsmS6c.jpg&h=6d41b599&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n豬肉問題，其實A先生清楚知道<br />\n一直主要用泰國豬肉健康農場，唔夠貨先會用利豐<br />\n但卻講一半唔講一半<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9SzP10w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9SzP10w.png&h=20b55961&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etvom0x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fetvom0x.png&h=27d6c84d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一直對A先生有絕對的信任<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a7CVc7A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa7CVc7A.png&h=01ba9b92&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7XdxfkW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7XdxfkW.png&h=8728c3fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iaJJm0X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiaJJm0X.png&h=bb9576ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rfOEEND.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrfOEEND.png&h=abc88be7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a4ba4023d9092ba392aedfa8c6663be6e775b99","tid":2513841,"uid":252318,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:50:11.000Z","msg":"我只係想講見到個廚房咁撚污糟已經唔會想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0624d65068fc42e141e4fbb6a229f6d804a0f410","tid":2513841,"uid":358135,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:53:40.000Z","msg":"兩個都係仆街<br />\n但係俾人炒撚咗嗰個戇鳩仔好似更加仆街"},{"pid":"bb9647ee5e35cfedb9bbf99c9b54cb13861c6ff7","tid":2513841,"uid":15097,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:55:23.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 攞員工資料威脅人<br />\n你間野都係食人血架啦<br />\n快撚d執左執啦"},{"pid":"bb31df56ac8e54b00641ab59b2bb9c777d37b798","tid":2513841,"uid":3873,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:56:22.000Z","msg":"先唔講勞資糾紛黃藍之類，間鋪咁撚多老鼠你叫人點放心食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b20159f2efe74543bc087b0562324193a9350e","tid":2513841,"uid":232540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:58:06.000Z","msg":"又開始賣慘賣黃賣人血咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留下言睇下啲豬豬受唔受先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81c53d955ea2be510ff05ba269b2eaa6b0e94c3","tid":2513841,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:58:36.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">當然我都無諗過我心目中嘅朋友會quote一段勞工法例畀我，除左心寒，我真係唔知可以講咩</span><br />\n出嚟打工講心唔講金<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b642a3905ba2e0953736472d9e7925da093f38d0","tid":2513841,"uid":46003,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5a4ba4023d9092ba392aedfa8c6663be6e775b99","tid":2513841,"uid":252318,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:50:11.000Z","msg":"我只係想講見到個廚房咁撚污糟已經唔會想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:59:22.000Z","msg":"由11月尾我地已經開始搵滅鼠公司處理問題<br />\n但鼠患問題唔係一時三刻可以解決到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地每晚都會清潔廚房以及洗地，<br />\n向大家保證，本店(包括前員工)唔會生產任何污糟食品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85a285a1ffe73a598d39b2648d88eeccd69cbcd","tid":2513841,"uid":8572,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T01:01:59.000Z","msg":"我必須承認，自己唔係一個擅於溝通嘅人，經常會詞不達意，令其他人誤會。<br />\n<br />\n話用網絡力量去攬炒人地 又話有晒人地個人資料都都誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e640da76c02b823a5c457a056aca33e561bd13d3","tid":2513841,"uid":243106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T01:02:15.000Z","msg":"唔賺錢仲開，真係求打個和<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a2b0641ee4cbd86cd737a3d6427ee94ab90c47c","tid":2513841,"uid":67425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T01:02:27.000Z","msg":"由包餃子賣腸粉嗰刻 就唔諗有冇賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且你仲想暗示人哋可能穿櫃桶底?<br />\n<br />\n你有冇裝cam?"},{"pid":"efe7b71219ec3d9db86bc372485ee0c31d0ef81c","tid":2513841,"uid":67425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d85a285a1ffe73a598d39b2648d88eeccd69cbcd","tid":2513841,"uid":8572,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T01:01:59.000Z","msg":"我必須承認，自己唔係一個擅於溝通嘅人，經常會詞不達意，令其他人誤會。<br />\n<br />\n話用網絡力量去攬炒人地 又話有晒人地個人資料都都誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T01:03:04.000Z","msg":"一切誤會嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2509de4a777dbf24d4267f95a467bf84bd43cd1c","tid":2513841,"uid":8572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e640da76c02b823a5c457a056aca33e561bd13d3","tid":2513841,"uid":243106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T01:02:15.000Z","msg":"唔賺錢仲開，真係求打個和<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T01:03:52.000Z","msg":"分享包餃子既喜悅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5477ac43f487b3d27236117cba9bf441747b795","tid":2513841,"uid":24523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T01:03:52.000Z","msg":"講到咁負責有處理鼠患問題<br />\n即係隔離post咁多人食到肚痛肚痾唔關老鼠事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係變壞咗嘅肉同過期嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e80553611d371c24fcaadaed8d1a2b162e82278","tid":2513841,"uid":67425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e640da76c02b823a5c457a056aca33e561bd13d3","tid":2513841,"uid":243106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T01:02:15.000Z","msg":"唔賺錢仲開，真係求打個和<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T01:04:36.000Z","msg":"米奇用曾志偉把聲講 <span class=\"xx-large\">打和！</span>"},{"pid":"ffb51f06d7222b6025ba2fca92407362cb7230df","tid":2513841,"uid":47029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"91b20159f2efe74543bc087b0562324193a9350e","tid":2513841,"uid":232540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:58:06.000Z","msg":"又開始賣慘賣黃賣人血咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留下言睇下啲豬豬受唔受先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T01:04:53.000Z","msg":"第一段d情緒勒索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0587f992970